title: R and R Bakery and Coffee Shoppe
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, American, Take-out, Bakery, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. R&R Bakery and Coffee Shoppe owners are vegans and make vegan muffins and cookies, vegan lunch food, and a daily v-plate that's vegan. Serves Starbucks brand coffee. Housed in a refurbished building with brick and dark wood, on the square in downtown Marshall.
